' Notes
note right of UC1
    Allows scheduling of
    appointments with automatic
    conflict detection
end note

note right of UC18
    Emergency reports trigger
    immediate notifications to
    on-call veterinarians
end note

note right of UC11
    Creates comprehensive
    diagnosis with treatment
    plan and medications
end note

note bottom of UC27
    Critical emergencies send
    alerts via SMS and email
    within 2 minutes
end note

note right of UC7
    Completing appointment can
    trigger invoice generation,
    diagnosis creation, and
    follow-up scheduling
end note

